        <briefdescription>
<para>Runs the Qt event loop for the skrat application. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>Sets application metadata, applies saved UI theme, optionally sets the window icon from the macOS bundle, constructs <ref refid="classMainWindow" kindref="compound">MainWindow</ref>, and if a path is passed as the first argument, opens that folder or selects that file in the tree.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">argc</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Number of elements in <emphasis>argv</emphasis> (including the program name). </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
<parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername direction="in">argv</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>Argument vector; <computeroutput>argv</computeroutput>[1] may be an initial folder or file path. </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para>Exit code from QApplication::exec() (typically 0 on normal quit). </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
